{"tid":1740552,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實今朝嘅黎明行動只係令到香港人等耐咗車同遲咗返到公司","createTime":"2019-11-20T03:29:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T09:42:07.000Z","uid":57786,"like":9,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"446e1e7870f08df273b66c457939dc224c42933e","tid":1740552,"uid":57786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T03:29:12.000Z","msg":"之前嘅風吹到好多人想被罷工<br />\n然後肯出嚟各區開花<br />\n而最成功係上星期三斷路斷鐵<br />\n但現實並唔係咁<br />\n而係變咗home office隨時on call<br />\n通返車又要返<br />\n有心開花又點會被份工綁住<br />\n<br />\n唔係話割但真心想知到底有乜用"},{"pid":"659490b1f233c9a1f906b81dfd23ba62cbeb380b","tid":1740552,"uid":57786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T03:29:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0ffb1ca4e32e4d6157fcfa74fa80153efaf9a69","tid":1740552,"uid":57786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T03:29:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbfb701578fee2289770f0d379621bf4ad8d1071","tid":1740552,"uid":57786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T03:29:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c3adb2c7980dc607e16e1918b27d629f46d0319","tid":1740552,"uid":57786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T03:30:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"813ab4f00ca13dab02b2023008b034e27a071dab","tid":1740552,"uid":144084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T03:32:23.000Z","msg":"無正面建樹 PO<br />\n士氣-1 <br />\n拉"},{"pid":"c4828b76024fffdeef42756937481fe704c88cdd","tid":1740552,"uid":54303,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T03:34:02.000Z","msg":"事實就係大家唔可以塞，要<span style=\"color: red;\">破壞</span><br />\n破壞交通樞紐之餘、仲要破壞電力、網絡供應，令到人地番到寫字樓都做唔到野"},{"pid":"e5f2764d6f15ad5ce4d5181b386dc05b3016040c","tid":1740552,"uid":42740,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T03:35:03.000Z","msg":"等香港老細習慣左打工仔唔再固定返到工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0605a4c6b7bfdaacdb030b9490c830484c5bdc2","tid":1740552,"uid":321238,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T03:39:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/026FRTK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F026FRTK.jpg&h=ba0c70f4&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">聰明啲，踢走班狗，先再搞啦！</span></span>"},{"pid":"94efa0bb2fbde0154012cc279f9ead3a0f61c5a3","tid":1740552,"uid":14337,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T03:41:14.000Z","msg":"其實好難日日被罷工<br />\n只有發自真心去罷工<br />\n先可以長期 先有效<br />\n其實手足已經做左好多<br />\n如果咁都唔罷工 都冇計"},{"pid":"913c6cbf9a893bb213c7ba77b1a70b34a9bc3dae","tid":1740552,"uid":289259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"446e1e7870f08df273b66c457939dc224c42933e","tid":1740552,"uid":57786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T03:29:12.000Z","msg":"之前嘅風吹到好多人想被罷工<br />\n然後肯出嚟各區開花<br />\n而最成功係上星期三斷路斷鐵<br />\n但現實並唔係咁<br />\n而係變咗home office隨時on call<br />\n通返車又要返<br />\n有心開花又點會被份工綁住<br />\n<br />\n唔係話割但真心想知到底有乜用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T03:50:30.000Z","msg":"各位手足，關於送林奠去大灣區的partition，尋日激增20000幾人(差不多簽署人數的10%)!，證明大家都好希望將佢舉家永遠封印晌大灣區！<br />\n<br />\n嘅然係咁就唔好停了，跟據早前民意調查有7成人唔妥佢嘅，咁我地嘅目標係咪應該set晌490萬個簽名呢？<br />\n<br />\n小弟英文唔好，如果可以的話，亦希望各手足可以幫手將佢推上國際！<br />\n<br />\n唔使俾錢架，簽完再share就唔使比錢㗎啦。<span style=\"color: red;\">最新消息：今朝22萬9千了！目標：490萬</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/uk-home-office-uk-home-office-should-revoke-carrie-lam-s-family-citizenship?cs_tk=AtIXNHLitQ7NOzo40F0AAXicyyvNyQEABF8BvKv03Ej5HuubaSSmIizKZKU%3D&amp;utm_campaign=514ad83a9aaf489a936c80aa7705b65d&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_source=recruit_sign_digest&amp;utm_term=cs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fuk-home-office-uk-home-office-should-revoke-carrie-lam-s-family-citizenship%3Fcs_tk%3DAtIXNHLitQ7NOzo40F0AAXicyyvNyQEABF8BvKv03Ej5HuubaSSmIizKZKU%253D%26utm_campaign%3D514ad83a9aaf489a936c80aa7705b65d%26utm_medium%3Demail%26utm_source%3Drecruit_sign_digest%26utm_term%3Dcs&d=qnfk3FWFLoR313jZLhvcNmZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=a4ab4278\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/uk-home-office-uk-home-office-should-revoke-carrie-lam-s-family-citizenship?cs_tk=AtIXNHLitQ7NOzo40F0AAXicyyvNyQEABF8BvKv03Ej5HuubaSSmIizKZKU%3D&amp;utm_campaign=514ad83a9aaf489a936c80aa7705b65d&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_source=recruit_sign_digest&amp;utm_term=cs</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hs8wPcW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHs8wPcW.jpg&h=66458b29&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d3c26e01a66669be4c736010c1195912847a9f29","tid":1740552,"uid":65353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T04:25:29.000Z","msg":"所以唔該聽日比心機<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e5MRYPW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe5MRYPW.png&h=dca5c76e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d23326690852b9f70f1efb9031f2a0eee692ed27","tid":1740552,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T04:26:19.000Z","msg":"增加返工人士對學生怨氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38ba85dac9e8cd46d7a72d138f2e932a6745bf75","tid":1740552,"uid":136431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T04:28:30.000Z","msg":"其實冇工會形式自發罷工，咩都係假<br />\n香港人太撚好適應力，你畀到少少阻礙佢，佢會諗百幾個方法去迴避。只不過係幫佢哋轉四至六小時工作週，大不了就Home Office，未形成到一個罷工嘅力量。<br />\n<br />\n工會真係不可或缺"},{"pid":"fb2a7058d1757d4e98182fb35dcbecba499f622d","tid":1740552,"uid":136431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38ba85dac9e8cd46d7a72d138f2e932a6745bf75","tid":1740552,"uid":136431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T04:28:30.000Z","msg":"其實冇工會形式自發罷工，咩都係假<br />\n香港人太撚好適應力，你畀到少少阻礙佢，佢會諗百幾個方法去迴避。只不過係幫佢哋轉四至六小時工作週，大不了就Home Office，未形成到一個罷工嘅力量。<br />\n<br />\n工會真係不可或缺"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T04:28:55.000Z","msg":"工作日*"},{"pid":"04b1f98f4df5e86ecd70ca965a61249fb68e6dfd","tid":1740552,"uid":130797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4828b76024fffdeef42756937481fe704c88cdd","tid":1740552,"uid":54303,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T03:34:02.000Z","msg":"事實就係大家唔可以塞，要<span style=\"color: red;\">破壞</span><br />\n破壞交通樞紐之餘、仲要破壞電力、網絡供應，令到人地番到寫字樓都做唔到野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T04:32:54.000Z","msg":"破壞完記得唔好再守<br />\n做完就去第二度做第二d工作<br />\n<br />\n有d交通工具或者公路壞左 停半日 塞一日<br />\n第二日可以俾下人返工<br />\n到第三日又破壞返 停半日 塞一日<br />\n第四日又可能有得返工<br />\n<br />\n被阻返工被罷工既事係唔可以好似上星期咁被養成習慣<br />\n間唔中俾返d返得到工既希望大家<br />\n和你塞先可以長長久久<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"827fc280155ce1020ff96263111ac8d5aed3913a","tid":1740552,"uid":138814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T04:36:33.000Z","msg":"喺地鐵上面大大聲播中共國歌<br />\nInception<br />\n將塞車、塞鐵同中共連埋一齊"},{"pid":"e34436fd402024585341845d2e414472f34454b6","tid":1740552,"uid":163620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T04:37:22.000Z","msg":"呢個就係自願罷工同迫人罷工分別，不過連登已經無人聽"},{"pid":"995050cbe9b3cadfeceaec1f5d6098672e9e0180","tid":1740552,"uid":51127,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e34436fd402024585341845d2e414472f34454b6","tid":1740552,"uid":163620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T04:37:22.000Z","msg":"呢個就係自願罷工同迫人罷工分別，不過連登已經無人聽"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T04:41:12.000Z","msg":"未見過歷史有人搞革命係搞到自己越黎越多敵人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63b5cac0d0b554a89ca32ab038661d3be2c94ece","tid":1740552,"uid":605